## ğŸ¯ Features

* âœ… Gujarati-style syntax: `sharu`, `jo`, `samaapt`, `lakho`, `jaano`, and more!
* ğŸ§  Beginner-friendly & readable structure
* ğŸ§ª Comes with its own Lexer, Parser, and Evaluator
