## ğŸ§ª Dev / Backend Usage

KemLang uses FastAPI to serve execution requests.

### Run API Locally:

```bash
uvicorn cli:app --reload
```

Then POST code to `http://localhost:8000/run` with:

```json
{
  "code": "sharu { lakho(\"KemLang\"); } samaapt"
}
```

